<para>This function initiates both the write and read channels of the VDMA associated with the specified <ref refid="struct_x_vproc_ss" kindref="compound">XVprocSs</ref> instance. It checks if the VDMA pointer is valid before starting the DMA operations.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
